Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.36,0:00:54.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在明白了\N{\fs24\1c}I see now
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.57,0:00:56.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大冰封杀死了我所认识的每个人时\N{\fs24\1c}that as The Freeze killed everyone I ever knew,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.53,0:01:00.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我错把生存的机会当成了自由\N{\fs24\1c}I mistook my ticket to survival for freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.45,0:01:03.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但正义没有上车\N{\fs24\1c}But justice never boarded,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.66,0:01:07.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威尔福德用守卫压迫我们\N{\fs24\1c}and Wilford doubled down with a Jackboot on our throats
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.29,0:01:09.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只手操控一切\N{\fs24\1c}and a fat finger on the scales.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.21,0:01:15.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而今 我们中有些人想改变他的要求\N{\fs24\1c}Now some of us are ready to change his terms.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.34,0:01:17.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过程将危险而肮脏\N{\fs24\1c}It will be perilous, filthy work.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.13,0:01:20.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将有更多珍贵生命逝去\N{\fs24\1c}More precious souls may be lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.14,0:01:21.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克雷 我不想惹麻烦\N{\fs24\1c}Clay, I don't want any trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.18,0:01:23.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是在工作 我不能卷进去\N{\fs24\1c}I'm just trying to work. I can't be involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.06,0:01:25.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你住在三等厢 这由不得你\N{\fs24\1c}You live in Third. You are involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.81,0:01:28.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们走到这一步 承受了那么多\N{\fs24\1c}But we didn't come this far, suffer this much
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.60,0:01:31.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不会向当初\N{\fs24\1c}to give in to the same tyranny
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.48,0:01:32.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毁了我们的暴行屈服\N{\fs24\1c}that destroyed us in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.11,0:01:38.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是在冰封的死亡星球上 人类也需要希望\N{\fs24\1c}Even on a frozen, dead planet, humanity needs hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.53,0:01:43.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这是我们在雪国列车上的革命\N{\fs24\1c}For these are our revolutions on Snowpiercer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.83,0:01:45.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1001节车厢的革命\N{\fs24\1c}1,001 cars long.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.68,0:01:58.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord1\fs38\b1}雪国列车\N第一季 第五集
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.83,0:02:29.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是你妻子做的吗\N{\fs24\1c}Did your wife make that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.50,0:02:31.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们结婚多久了\N{\fs24\1c}How long have you been married?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.51,0:02:41.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你妻子叫什么\N{\fs24\1c}What's your wife's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.63,0:02:43.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在哪认识的\N{\fs24\1c}Where'd you guys meet?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.31,0:02:49.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里待了这么久 你还是不肯跟我说话吗\N{\fs24\1c}All this time in here, and you still won't talk to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.35,0:02:52.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在这里说的话可以作为呈堂证供\N{\fs24\1c}What you say in here is admissible.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.19,0:02:54.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那又如何\N{\fs24\1c}So?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.31,0:02:56.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以聪明的来客都闭上嘴\N{\fs24\1c}So our smart visitors stay quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.52,0:02:59.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是有罪的来客 我无可隐瞒\N{\fs24\1c}Your guilty visitors do. I have nothing to hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.78,0:03:07.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我父母是在瑞士圣莫里茨的缆椅上相识的\N{\fs24\1c}My parents met in St. Moritz, on a chairlift.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.16,0:03:09.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你父母是谁\N{\fs24\1c}I know who your parents are.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.91,0:03:12.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 你不知道 但你会知道的\N{\fs24\1c}No. No, you don't. But you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.54,0:03:17.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小莱 亲爱的 你没事吧\N{\fs24\1c}LJ, honey. Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.92,0:03:19.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要带你回家\N{\fs24\1c}Oh, we are taking you home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.21,0:03:22.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-梅兰妮 -亲爱的 我们好想你\N{\fs24\1c}- Melanie. - Sweetheart, we miss you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.01,0:03:23.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要跟我们回家\N{\fs24\1c}You're coming home with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.72,0:03:25.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小莱 你今天将接受谋杀审判\N{\fs24\1c}LJ, today you stand trial for murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.68,0:03:27.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明白吗\N{\fs24\1c}Do you understand that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.89,0:03:29.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs24\1c}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.77,0:03:32.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要代表自己发言\N{\fs24\1c}You'll be expected to speak on your own behalf,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.73,0:03:35.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由有票乘客组成的法庭将给出判决\N{\fs24\1c}and a tribunal of ticketed passengers will render a verdict.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.27,0:03:36.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了吗\N{\fs24\1c}Is that all clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.06,0:03:39.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威尔福德先生将会密切关注进展\N{\fs24\1c}Mr. Wilford will be following closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.48,0:03:42.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 那他就能看到这一切多么荒唐\N{\fs24\1c}Good. Then he can see how ridiculous this whole thing is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.94,0:03:44.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去跟三名被害人所在的三等厢说啊\N{\fs24\1c}Tell it to Third, where the three victims lived.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.74,0:03:52.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她还是个孩子\N{\fs24\1c}She's just a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.66,0:03:54.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犯罪的人已经死了\N{\fs24\1c}The man who committed these crimes is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.79,0:03:56.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而你把她关进了监狱\N{\fs24\1c}You just threw her in a cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.04,0:03:59.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道这在前车引发了怎样的反响吗\N{\fs24\1c}Do you have any idea how this is playing uptrain?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.92,0:04:02.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按照列车规矩 我们必须在审判前扣押她\N{\fs24\1c}We are bound by train rules to detain her ahead of trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.01,0:04:04.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仅此而已 莱拉\N{\fs24\1c}That's all, Lilah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.89,0:04:08.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-没事的 -我不该进抽屉\N{\fs24\1c}- It's okay. - I don't belong in a drawer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.85,0:04:12.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请送他们回房\N{\fs24\1c}Please escort them to their quarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.39,0:04:17.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想感谢威尔福德先生给我机会证明这一点\N{\fs24\1c}And I just want to thank Mr. Wilford for the chance to prove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.53,0:04:29.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得法庭判她有罪的可能性有多大\N{\fs24\1c}What are the chances you figure that the tribunal convicts her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.83,0:04:34.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他们放了她 三等厢会动乱的\N{\fs24\1c}There's gonna be trouble in Third if they let her off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.16,0:04:36.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经有乱子了\N{\fs24\1c}There already is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.96,0:04:40.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来感染有所好转\N{\fs24\1c}It looks like the infection's improving.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.05,0:04:46.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的扑克脸需要练习了 医生\N{\fs24\1c}Your poker face needs work, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.01,0:04:48.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以前是兽医\N{\fs24\1c}I was a vet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.84,0:04:50.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的病人不会顶嘴\N{\fs24\1c}My patients didn't talk back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.31,0:04:56.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有消息\N{\fs24\1c}Message!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.02,0:04:59.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿斯特丽德又传来一条\N{\fs24\1c}Astrid sent another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.65,0:05:02.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"今天"\N{\fs24\1c}"Today"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.11,0:05:04.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她想让我今天就去前车\N{\fs24\1c}She wants me uptrain today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.44,0:05:06.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她一定是有莱顿的消息了\N{\fs24\1c}She must have some news on Layton.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.03,0:05:07.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备好了吗 牛人\N{\fs24\1c}You ready, badass?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.74,0:05:11.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把芯片放在手链里\N{\fs24\1c}Put the chip in this bracelet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.20,0:05:12.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要往上戴一些\N{\fs24\1c}Make sure you wear it nice and high.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.58,0:05:15.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-就像其他人一样在面板上刷一下 -好\N{\fs24\1c}- You're chipping the pad just like anyone else. - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.75,0:05:17.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心点\N{\fs24\1c}Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.50,0:05:24.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这枚芯片可以让你进入二等厢\N{\fs24\1c}This chip will get you into Second Class.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.18,0:05:33.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成珍珠 作为此名升舱申请人的担保人\N{\fs24\1c}Jinju Seong, as Surety for this Upgrade Applicant,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.39,0:05:35.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要为她在试用期中的行为\N{\fs24\1c}you accept liability for her conduct
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.39,0:05:37.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,承担责任 明白了吗\N{\fs24\1c}during her probationary period, understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.52,0:05:42.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白 要是她乱来 我们都会遭殃\N{\fs24\1c}Yeah, if she messes up, we both suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.23,0:05:43.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白\N{\fs24\1c}Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.82,0:05:47.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-这样就行了 贝丝 -谢谢 医生\N{\fs24\1c}- That should do it, Bess. - Thanks, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.24,0:05:49.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有你的\N{\fs24\1c}And yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.79,0:05:57.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了\N{\fs24\1c}Okay, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.83,0:06:00.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我谨代表威尔福德工业\N{\fs24\1c}On behalf of Wilford Industries,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.25,0:06:02.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在此授予你 贝丝·弗朗西斯·提尔\N{\fs24\1c}I hereby grant you, Bess Francis Till,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.96,0:06:06.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进入二等厢 以及其附带的所有权利\N{\fs24\1c}access to Second Class and all the entitlements therein.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.71,0:06:08.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\fs24\1c}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.84,0:06:11.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们让你们俩好好庆祝一下\N{\fs24\1c}Well, I guess we should leave you two to celebrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.69,0:06:22.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看我们\N{\fs24\1c}Look at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.65,0:06:27.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,足足过了三个月才开始同居\N{\fs24\1c}Made it three whole months before shacking up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.44,0:06:29.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的个人最佳纪录\N{\fs24\1c}Personal best for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.66,0:06:33.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你确定要这么做吗\N{\fs24\1c}You sure about all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.66,0:06:36.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二等厢和附带的所有权利吗 不\N{\fs24\1c}Second Class and all the entitlements therein? No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.04,0:06:41.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但从我们认识那天起 我就要定你了\N{\fs24\1c}But I was sure about you the day we met.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.01,0:06:50.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人会给她定罪的\N{\fs24\1c}No one's going to convict her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.09,0:06:51.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,审判员都是付费乘客\N{\fs24\1c}The tribunal is paid passengers,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.99,0:06:53.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一等二等厢 我们都认识\N{\fs24\1c}First and Second. We know them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.72,0:06:56.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就等你准备好了 宝贝\N{\fs24\1c}As long as you're prepared, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.97,0:06:59.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她会准备好的\N{\fs24\1c}She'll be prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.98,0:07:02.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但在证人席上世事难料\N{\fs24\1c}But things happen on the stand --
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.52,0:07:04.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-小莱 -注意听 宝贝\N{\fs24\1c}- LJ. - Pay attention, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.44,0:07:04.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别玩了\N{\fs24\1c}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.99,0:07:11.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们觉得抽屉里是什么样的\N{\fs24\1c}What do you think it's like in The Drawers?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.40,0:07:14.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不用担心这些\N{\fs24\1c}Oh, you don't have to worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.24,0:07:17.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚一切就都结束了 你会回到我们身边\N{\fs24\1c}By tonight, this will all be over and you'll be back here with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.45,0:07:18.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸\N{\fs24\1c}Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.12,0:07:20.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以吗\N{\fs24\1c}Can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.96,0:07:24.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不行 小莱\N{\fs24\1c}Not now, LJ.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.33,0:07:26.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要\N{\fs24\1c}I want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.50,0:07:27.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的\N{\fs24\1c}It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.15,0:07:51.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看\N{\fs24\1c}Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.20,0:07:56.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 够了\N{\fs24\1c}Okay. That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.87,0:07:58.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吐出来\N{\fs24\1c}Spit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.45,0:08:01.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天可不是胡闹的时候\N{\fs24\1c}It's not a day for your antics.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.83,0:08:07.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你嘴里只应该吐出来这些字\N{\fs24\1c}The only thing that should be in your mouth are these words --
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.79,0:08:09.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"他逼我的"\N{\fs24\1c}"He forced me."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.09,0:08:10.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确是他逼我的\N{\fs24\1c}He did force me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.88,0:08:14.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们知道的吧\N{\fs24\1c}You do know that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.84,0:08:15.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们知道 宝贝\N{\fs24\1c}We know, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.22,0:08:18.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们知道\N{\fs24\1c}We know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.52,0:08:34.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特里斯坦 请在休息时间看窗外的风景\N{\fs24\1c}Tristan, stare out the window on your own time, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.24,0:08:37.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我曾经梦想有一天能看到亚马逊\N{\fs24\1c}Sorry. I used to dream I'd see the Amazon someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.86,0:08:40.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在那里除了冰块什么都没有了\N{\fs24\1c}Well, there's nothing out there now but frozen lump.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.66,0:08:44.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等所有人都走了 我要你像平常的布置一样\N{\fs24\1c}As soon as everyone's gone, I want you to set up for the tribunal,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.95,0:08:46.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备一下法庭\N{\fs24\1c}as per the usual floor plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.75,0:08:47.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 夫人\N{\fs24\1c}Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.65,0:09:09.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菜已经上完了\N{\fs24\1c}Service is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.69,0:09:11.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么\N{\fs24\1c}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.73,0:09:14.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么\N{\fs24\1c}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.61,0:09:17.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请享用 夜车招待的\N{\fs24\1c}Enjoy. Compliments of the Nightcar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.36,0:09:20.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙玛先生 等一下\N{\fs24\1c}Mr. Sharma, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.20,0:09:25.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊 我...\N{\fs24\1c}My God. I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.70,0:09:27.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立刻把梅兰妮找来\N{\fs24\1c}Go and get Melanie. Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.80,0:09:40.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做出那种事有失身份 奥德丽\N{\fs24\1c}That stunt was beneath you, Audrey.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.09,0:09:42.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 并不失身份\N{\fs24\1c}No, it really wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.27,0:09:48.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮基的事我很遗憾\N{\fs24\1c}I'm sorry about Nikki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.19,0:09:51.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的\N{\fs24\1c}I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.19,0:09:53.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但一个嫌犯死了\N{\fs24\1c}But one suspect is dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.11,0:09:57.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一个正以谋杀罪受审 我还漏了什么\N{\fs24\1c}and the other is standing trial for murder. What am I missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.32,0:09:59.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道那审判就是个笑话\N{\fs24\1c}You know the trial is a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.07,0:10:02.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在五英里外的前厢 由一等和二等厢组成的陪审团\N{\fs24\1c}It's five miles uptrain, where a jury of First and Second
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.95,0:10:05.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将审判他们自己人是否杀了我们三个人\N{\fs24\1c}get to judge one of their own for killing three of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.67,0:10:06.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们\N{\fs24\1c}Us?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.46,0:10:12.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夜车应该保持中立才对\N{\fs24\1c}The Nightcar is supposed to be Switzerland.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.88,0:10:15.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么把这事政治化\N{\fs24\1c}Why are you politicizing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.68,0:10:22.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三等厢有权请愿威尔福德\N{\fs24\1c}Third has the right to petition Wilford
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.51,0:10:25.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要涉及到劳动纠纷和审判规程事宜\N{\fs24\1c}in labor disputes and matters of jurisprudence.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.35,0:10:26.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们希望设立新法庭\N{\fs24\1c}We want a new tribunal drawn --
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.43,0:10:29.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每个车厢各派出一名代表\N{\fs24\1c}one representative from each class
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.60,0:10:31.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及组建一个代表团 旁观审判\N{\fs24\1c}and a delegation to observe the trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.65,0:10:35.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老天 奥德丽\N{\fs24\1c}For Christ's sake, Audrey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.61,0:10:39.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听命于威尔福德使你变得冷酷无情\N{\fs24\1c}You've grown callous doing Wilford's bidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.07,0:10:46.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以前也曾试图改变现状\N{\fs24\1c}You used to try to make a difference, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.75,0:10:50.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我当时就站在这\N{\fs24\1c}And I stood right here
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.12,0:10:52.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听你分享你对夜车的愿景\N{\fs24\1c}when you shared your vision of the Nightcar.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.25,0:10:56.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威尔福德只看见妓院\N{\fs24\1c}Wilford saw a brothel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.75,0:10:59.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而你看见了更高的目标\N{\fs24\1c}And you saw a higher purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.34,0:11:02.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说服了他 我是对的\N{\fs24\1c}And you persuaded him I was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.09,0:11:05.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我请求你忠于你的愿景\N{\fs24\1c}And I am asking you to stay true to your vision.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.22,0:11:08.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你给了我们一个熬过悲伤的地方\N{\fs24\1c}You give us a place to work through our grief,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.43,0:11:10.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,列车依靠它\N{\fs24\1c}and the train depends on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.68,0:11:14.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我们依靠你 靠你向威尔福德发声\N{\fs24\1c}And we depend on you, on your voice to Wilford's ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.77,0:11:18.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向他建议设立新法庭\N{\fs24\1c}Recommend a new tribunal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.69,0:11:20.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否则怎么样\N{\fs24\1c}Or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.99,0:11:24.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别逼我威胁你 梅兰妮\N{\fs24\1c}Don't make me threaten you, Melanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.03,0:11:28.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三等厢和列车上所有系统都有联系\N{\fs24\1c}Third touches every system on this train.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.99,0:11:30.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的声音必被听见\N{\fs24\1c}We will be heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.09,0:11:47.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长期假死对妮基造成了什么影响\N{\fs24\1c}What has the long-term suspension done to Nikki?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.76,0:11:49.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以告诉你生理效应\N{\fs24\1c}I can tell you the physiological effects --
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.26,0:11:53.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肾上腺组织坏死 肝功能不全\N{\fs24\1c}necrosis of adrenal tissue, hepatic insufficiencies.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.98,0:11:56.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的精神状态呢\N{\fs24\1c}But her mental state?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.23,0:11:59.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说不好她本来会不会改善\N{\fs24\1c}I can't say whether she would have improved or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.15,0:12:04.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没足够时间让她完全脱瘾\N{\fs24\1c}There wasn't enough time to detox her fully.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.44,0:12:06.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是否假设他们正有\N{\fs24\1c}Are we assuming they're experiencing something
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.40,0:12:08.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-类似闭锁综合征的体验 -也许吧\N{\fs24\1c}- like Locked-in Syndrome? - Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.03,0:12:12.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得从减慢唤醒他们的速度开始\N{\fs24\1c}We need to start by reviving them much slower.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.74,0:12:14.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有四百个抽屉\N{\fs24\1c}We have 400 drawers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.33,0:12:15.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一天也许会有四百名沉睡者\N{\fs24\1c}Someday we may have 400 Sleepers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.91,0:12:18.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们不能再出现时精神受创\N{\fs24\1c}They can't re-emerge traumatized.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.92,0:12:24.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转告威尔福德先生 我在努力了\N{\fs24\1c}Tell Mr. Wilford I'm trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.88,0:12:26.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\fs24\1c}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.26,0:12:30.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还好吧\N{\fs24\1c}You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.72,0:12:33.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说三等厢正请愿在法庭上占有一席之位\N{\fs24\1c}I hear Third are petitioning for a spot on the tribunal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.64,0:12:37.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在考虑这事吗\N{\fs24\1c}Are you considering it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.35,0:12:41.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小莱也许能获判应有的罪名\N{\fs24\1c}LJ may actually get what she deserves.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.73,0:12:43.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你确实在考虑\N{\fs24\1c}You are considering it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.70,0:12:49.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让三等厢的人参与审判\N{\fs24\1c}A Thirdie on the tribunal?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.62,0:12:52.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 头等厢的人不会满意\N{\fs24\1c}No, that's not gonna be popular in First.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.33,0:12:55.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头等厢和二等厢要有同样的代表\N{\fs24\1c}Equal representation with First and Second.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.41,0:12:56.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是要求\N{\fs24\1c}That's the demand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.37,0:12:58.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们疯了吗\N{\fs24\1c}Are you guys insane?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.62,0:13:01.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,福爵家族在头等厢势力很大 他们会吓坏的\N{\fs24\1c}The Folgers have a lot of power in First. They'll freak out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.38,0:13:03.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得我们现在有阶级分化了吗\N{\fs24\1c}You think we have a class divide now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.21,0:13:05.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可能会毁了一切\N{\fs24\1c}This could blow the whole thing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.02,0:13:10.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能借一步说话吗\N{\fs24\1c}Can I borrow you for a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.10,0:13:12.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行\N{\fs24\1c}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.51,0:13:15.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈维 你能来掌舵吗\N{\fs24\1c}Javi, can you take the helm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.22,0:13:17.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题\N{\fs24\1c}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.66,0:14:15.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自从蜜蜂死后我们就没干过了\N{\fs24\1c}We haven't done that since the bees died.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.87,0:14:22.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我似乎发现了一个模式\N{\fs24\1c}I'm sensing a bit of a pattern.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.79,0:14:26.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天呐 我真希望能开窗\N{\fs24\1c}God, I wish I could open a frigging window.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.46,0:14:30.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还记得新鲜空气吗\N{\fs24\1c}You remember fresh air?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.52,0:14:41.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你记得\N{\fs24\1c}You remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.94,0:14:45.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,散步吗\N{\fs24\1c}going for walks?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.20,0:14:53.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下雨\N{\fs24\1c}Rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.32,0:14:55.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想念雨声\N{\fs24\1c}I miss the sound of rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.83,0:15:01.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想念很多事情\N{\fs24\1c}I miss so many things.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.01,0:15:16.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要这么做吗\N{\fs24\1c}Are you gonna do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.72,0:15:20.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,设立一个新的法庭\N{\fs24\1c}Draw a new tribunal?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.43,0:15:24.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只想呼吸\N{\fs24\1c}I just want to breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.11,0:16:14.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位乘客请注意\N{\fs24\1c}Attention, passengers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.90,0:16:19.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威尔福德先生接受了三等厢的请求\N{\fs24\1c}Mr. Wilford has accepted a Third Class petition
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.16,0:16:22.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为今天的审讯重新设立一个法庭\N{\fs24\1c}to redraw the tribunal for today's trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.54,0:16:29.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将从每个车厢随机抽取一个人的名字\N{\fs24\1c}One name has been drawn randomly from each class.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.50,0:16:33.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你听到了自己的名字 请立即到\N{\fs24\1c}If your name is called, please report immediately
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.17,0:16:35.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乘客服务部代表处报道\N{\fs24\1c}to your Hospitality representative.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.38,0:16:41.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头等厢 陪审员是伊迪丝·古斯特菲尔德\N{\fs24\1c}From First Class, our jurist is Edith Gusterfeld.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.89,0:16:43.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二等厢\N{\fs24\1c}From Second Class,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.39,0:16:45.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小学老师玛丽-伊丽莎白·吉利斯\N{\fs24\1c}primary teacher Mary-Elizabeth Gillies.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.39,0:16:49.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三等厢的代表是\N{\fs24\1c}And representing Third Class --
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.02,0:16:52.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,造纸工人沃特·弗莱明\N{\fs24\1c}Papermaker Walter Flemming.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.28,0:16:55.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重复一次 伊迪丝·古斯特菲尔德\N{\fs24\1c}Again, Edith Gusterfeld,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.29,0:16:57.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽-伊丽莎白·吉利斯\N{\fs24\1c}Mary-Elizabeth Gillies,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.90,0:16:59.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-与沃特·弗莱明 -出发\N{\fs24\1c}- and Walter Flemming... - Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.37,0:17:02.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请立即到乘客服务部报道\N{\fs24\1c}...please report to Hospitality.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.49,0:17:04.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢各位\N{\fs24\1c}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.04,0:17:05.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们做到了\N{\fs24\1c}Oh, we did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.84,0:17:08.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五分钟后回去清洁\N{\fs24\1c}Back on Sanitation in five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.37,0:17:11.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点 快点\N{\fs24\1c}Come on. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.88,0:17:13.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想休息\N{\fs24\1c}I want a break, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.36,0:17:35.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是她\N{\fs24\1c}It's her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.03,0:17:38.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢天谢地 你做到了\N{\fs24\1c}Oh, thank God. You made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.11,0:17:42.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你发现了什么\N{\fs24\1c}What did you find out?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.49,0:17:45.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么可靠的信息 但如果他不在车尾\N{\fs24\1c}There's nothing solid, but if he's not in the Tail...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.54,0:17:47.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 那她去哪\N{\fs24\1c}Okay. So where's she going?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.91,0:17:49.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得我找到了一个能帮忙的人\N{\fs24\1c}I think I found someone who might help.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.04,0:17:52.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-谁 -一个保洁员 叫特伦斯\N{\fs24\1c}- Who? - The janitors, a guy named Terence.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.42,0:17:54.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给 快 好了 裤子\N{\fs24\1c}Here, quick. I got this. Pants.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.17,0:17:56.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着 那个守卫分不出我们的区别\N{\fs24\1c}Look. That Jack can't tell us apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.17,0:17:59.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会在下次休息前回来 我保证\N{\fs24\1c}I'll be back before the next break, I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.42,0:18:00.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-对 -好吗\N{\fs24\1c}- Yeah. - Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.38,0:18:03.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就保持低调 好吗\N{\fs24\1c}You just keep your head down, alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.14,0:18:05.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我们会帮你殿后 -好\N{\fs24\1c}- We'll watch your back. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.93,0:18:07.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从这过去 祝你们好运\N{\fs24\1c}Okay, go through here. Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.64,0:18:10.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我要去哪 -市场\N{\fs24\1c}- Where am I going? - The Market.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.23,0:18:12.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找黄色的蝴蝶 过去就能看到\N{\fs24\1c}Look for the yellow butterfly. You'll see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.35,0:18:14.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 谢谢\N{\fs24\1c}Okay. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.73,0:18:15.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望你找到他\N{\fs24\1c}I hope you find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.08,0:18:33.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗莱明先生\N{\fs24\1c}Mr. Flemming.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.38,0:18:36.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威尔福德先生感谢您的服务\N{\fs24\1c}Mr. Wilford thanks you for your service.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.50,0:18:38.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请自便\N{\fs24\1c}Please help yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.34,0:18:43.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不打声招呼吗\N{\fs24\1c}Not saying hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.89,0:18:45.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是玛丽 小学老师\N{\fs24\1c}I'm Mary, the primary teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.85,0:18:47.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我应该感谢您做的手工\N{\fs24\1c}I ought to thank you for your craft.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.31,0:18:49.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子们都很喜欢"新纸日"\N{\fs24\1c}The kids love New Paper Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.56,0:18:51.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊迪丝·古斯特菲尔德 头等厢的\N{\fs24\1c}Edith Gusterfeld, Firstie.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.94,0:18:53.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但别因此而反感我\N{\fs24\1c}But don't hold that against me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.65,0:18:54.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理解\N{\fs24\1c}Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.11,0:18:55.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我喜欢你的耳环 -谢谢 亲爱的\N{\fs24\1c}- I like your earrings. - Thank you, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.19,0:18:57.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古斯特菲尔德夫人...\N{\fs24\1c}Aww! Ms. Gusterfeld...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.90,0:18:59.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威尔福德先生难道不知道\N{\fs24\1c}Doesn't Mr. Wilford understand
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.48,0:19:02.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不能随便更改规则吗\N{\fs24\1c}that you can't just change the rules?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.61,0:19:04.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得这些规则他有权更改\N{\fs24\1c}I guess they're his rules to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.87,0:19:07.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他遵循人们的意愿\N{\fs24\1c}He chose the will of the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.91,0:19:10.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们没有意愿\N{\fs24\1c}We don't have will.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.96,0:19:13.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只有秩序\N{\fs24\1c}We have order.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.37,0:19:17.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不是每天都有机会和其他舱位的人交流的\N{\fs24\1c}It's not every day we get a chance to mingle with other classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.76,0:19:27.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三等车厢代表们 如果你们想参加审讯\N{\fs24\1c}Third Class delegates, if you want to go to to the trial,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.30,0:19:30.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就说出你们的名字和乘客号码\N{\fs24\1c}give me your names and passenger numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.77,0:19:36.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜\N{\fs24\1c}Well, congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.81,0:19:40.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定很开心你现在是中产阶级了\N{\fs24\1c}You must be happy now that you're bourgeoisie.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.78,0:19:43.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不一定 你今天要向瘾君子们进行性敲诈吗\N{\fs24\1c}That depends. Are you gonna extort addicts for sex today?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.24,0:19:47.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这样 我的缓刑已经过了\N{\fs24\1c}Come on, man. My probation's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.37,0:19:57.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 我想留下来看珍珠作证\N{\fs24\1c}Okay, well, I'd like to stay for Jinju's testimony,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.42,0:19:58.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给她一些支持\N{\fs24\1c}you know, show her some support.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.71,0:20:00.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前车准备好了\N{\fs24\1c}They're ready uptrain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.38,0:20:02.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们最好出发了 是不是\N{\fs24\1c}Well, better get going, then, shouldn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.76,0:20:06.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 邋遢鬼们\N{\fs24\1c}Alright, dirtbags!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.34,0:20:08.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要出发了 都听好了\N{\fs24\1c}We're on the march! Now, listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.81,0:20:12.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着 对\N{\fs24\1c}Listen! Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.52,0:20:13.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们即将在前列车厢看到\N{\fs24\1c}Now, you're gonna see some things uptrain
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.93,0:20:15.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一些你们不熟悉的东西\N{\fs24\1c}that are unfamiliar to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.60,0:20:18.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如卫生和自尊\N{\fs24\1c}things like hygiene and self-respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.48,0:20:22.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们会听到人们说出完整的句子\N{\fs24\1c}You will hear people speaking in complete sentences.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.36,0:20:24.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要去打他们 不要去抢他们的随身物品\N{\fs24\1c}Now, don't punch them. Don't punch their belongings.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.99,0:20:25.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要乱舔东西\N{\fs24\1c}Don't lick things.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.32,0:20:27.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说得够清楚吗\N{\fs24\1c}Am I making myself clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.78,0:20:29.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,双手放好 眼睛直视\N{\fs24\1c}Now, hands to yourself, eyes forward,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.99,0:20:32.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且记住谁才是指挥者 好吗\N{\fs24\1c}and just remember who's carrying the batons, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.24,0:20:33.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 够了\N{\fs24\1c}Alright. That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.04,0:20:36.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 大家请排成一队\N{\fs24\1c}Okay, everyone, in a line, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.17,0:20:39.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古斯特菲尔德夫人会跟着头等厢投票\N{\fs24\1c}Mrs. Gusterfeld will vote with First.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.63,0:20:41.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她会让老师也同意的\N{\fs24\1c}She'll get the teacher on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.48,0:20:43.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心\N{\fs24\1c}Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.09,0:20:46.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没有意识到发生了什么 是吧\N{\fs24\1c}You don't see what's happening, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.68,0:20:52.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有个想法正在前列车厢中传播 罗伯特\N{\fs24\1c}There's an idea traveling uptrain, Robert.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.81,0:20:55.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个想法想要持续存在\N{\fs24\1c}It wants to live, this idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.52,0:21:00.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它想点燃整个列车\N{\fs24\1c}It wants to set the train ablaze,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.56,0:21:02.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而它只需要一个小火花\N{\fs24\1c}and all it needs is a spark.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.69,0:21:05.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它只需要用它粗糙的手指\N{\fs24\1c}All it needs is to wrap its thick fingers
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.74,0:21:07.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掐住你女儿的脖子\N{\fs24\1c}around your daughter's throat
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.53,0:21:09.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了那个工人将她掐死\N{\fs24\1c}and choke her out for the working man.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.66,0:21:11.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fs24\1c}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.74,0:21:13.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都好 亲爱的\N{\fs24\1c}Everything's fine, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.04,0:21:16.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看起来好美\N{\fs24\1c}You look beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.87,0:21:18.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们继续来排练你的证词\N{\fs24\1c}Let's keep working on your testimony.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.17,0:21:23.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他的就交给我 莱拉\N{\fs24\1c}Leave the rest to me, Lilah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.76,0:21:32.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个变态的杀人团体又带走了一个人\N{\fs24\1c}That psycho's Kill Cult took another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.18,0:21:42.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们与上帝同行\N{\fs24\1c}Juntos, vamos con dios.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.10,0:21:45.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坚持住\N{\fs24\1c}Hang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.11,0:21:46.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个变态的杀人团体又带走了一个人\N{\fs24\1c}That psycho's Kill Cult took another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.90,0:21:49.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不 我们很饿 -但也不能这样\N{\fs24\1c}- No, we are hungry. - Not like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.99,0:21:51.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能闻到他们在做吃的\N{\fs24\1c}I can smell them cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.65,0:21:52.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们在后面 靠着墙\N{\fs24\1c}They're at the back now, against the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.20,0:21:54.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死的食人族\N{\fs24\1c}Goddamn cannibals.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.20,0:21:56.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 迈尔斯 上去吧\N{\fs24\1c}Come on, Miles. Up you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.70,0:21:59.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我们会没事的 -我们需要你帮忙\N{\fs24\1c}- We'll be alright. - We need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.87,0:22:01.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去阻止他们\N{\fs24\1c}Put a stop to them now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.62,0:22:05.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给\N{\fs24\1c}Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.48,0:23:07.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎来到三等厢\N{\fs24\1c}Welcome to Third.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.76,0:23:16.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她浑身散发着清洁小队的臭气\N{\fs24\1c}She reeks of Sanitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.54,0:23:18.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来你是这么出来的啊\N{\fs24\1c}So that's how you got out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.18,0:23:21.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿斯特丽德不肯说\N{\fs24\1c}Astrid wouldn't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.39,0:23:23.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fs24\1c}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.85,0:23:26.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们如此铤而走险就是为了找到莱顿\N{\fs24\1c}We risked this for one reason -- to find Layton.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.92,0:23:28.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他没回车尾吗\N{\fs24\1c}He's not back in the Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.78,0:23:30.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说是回了 但其实没有\N{\fs24\1c}They're saying he is, but, no, he isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.37,0:23:32.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们觉得他进了抽屉\N{\fs24\1c}We think he's in a drawer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.17,0:23:38.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说...\N{\fs24\1c}So, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.29,0:23:42.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个男人站了出来\N{\fs24\1c}the man comes forward,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.90,0:23:45.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,破解了列车史上最大的案子\N{\fs24\1c}solves the biggest crime in train history.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.80,0:23:47.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么还要把他关进抽屉呢\N{\fs24\1c}Why would they put him in a drawer?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.50,0:23:50.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许是他发现了不可告人的秘密\N{\fs24\1c}Maybe he turned over the wrong rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.29,0:23:51.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许他已经死了\N{\fs24\1c}Or maybe he's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.39,0:23:54.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许是他惹恼了威尔福德\N{\fs24\1c}Maybe he pissed off Wilford
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.95,0:23:58.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害自己被处死\N{\fs24\1c}and, uh, got his head stuck out a port, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.77,0:24:01.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是打不死的 你见过他\N{\fs24\1c}He's not the dying type. You met him.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.23,0:24:03.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有意思\N{\fs24\1c}Funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.48,0:24:07.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们刚刚正好聊到了抽屉的事\N{\fs24\1c}We were just talking about The Drawers.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.73,0:24:10.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们能进去吗\N{\fs24\1c}Can we get in?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.90,0:24:12.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天时机不错\N{\fs24\1c}Might not be a bad day for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.36,0:24:15.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为审判的事 安保很薄弱\N{\fs24\1c}Security's lean 'cause of the trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.95,0:24:18.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那...\N{\fs24\1c}Yeah, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.47,0:24:20.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,管他的\N{\fs24\1c}What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.46,0:24:22.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就去抽屉吧\N{\fs24\1c}Let's hit The Drawers.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.67,0:24:26.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们与三等厢的好人没有过节\N{\fs24\1c}We have no issue with the good people of Third,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.80,0:24:28.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果他们只想制造骚乱\N{\fs24\1c}but if all they have to do is make a bit of noise
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.38,0:24:30.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我们突然打算改写列车神圣的规矩\N{\fs24\1c}and suddenly we're rewriting the enshrined rules of the train,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.58,0:24:32.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们就都有麻烦了\N{\fs24\1c}then we all have a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.38,0:24:36.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恕我直言 福爵先生 你这么说\N{\fs24\1c}All due respect, Mr. Folger, are you speaking
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.63,0:24:40.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是出自一位担忧的公民 还是一位害怕的父亲\N{\fs24\1c}as a concerned citizen or a scared daddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.42,0:24:42.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-都有 -我们都支持福爵一家\N{\fs24\1c}- Both. - We all stand with the Folgers.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.16,0:24:45.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果三等厢针对我们的小孩 他们也会如此\N{\fs24\1c}As they'd stand with us if Third came for our children.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.25,0:24:51.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的职责是维持规矩 不是制定规矩\N{\fs24\1c}My job is to uphold the rules, not to make them.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.05,0:24:53.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威尔福德先生把自己封闭在了前车\N{\fs24\1c}Mr. Wilford locked himself away uptrain.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.33,0:24:54.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他与现实脱节了\N{\fs24\1c}The man is out of touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.67,0:24:57.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他有让我们所有人活下去的能力\N{\fs24\1c}He's got the skills to keep us all alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.76,0:24:58.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们有什么\N{\fs24\1c}What have you got?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.65,0:25:00.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有作为早期投资者身份的四亿美元\N{\fs24\1c}I got $400 million in early investor status
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.98,0:25:03.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及如果事关我的生死 我能制造很多麻烦\N{\fs24\1c}and a whole world of pain when it comes to my survival.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.43,0:25:05.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要误会我们\N{\fs24\1c}Please don't misunderstand us.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.55,0:25:08.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愿威尔福德的永动机永不停息\N{\fs24\1c}May Wilford run his engine for as long as the track holds.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.05,0:25:14.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但日常运行 正义 资源 车尾\N{\fs24\1c}But day-to-day operations, justice, resources, the Tail...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.80,0:25:16.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许这些问题在这里解决更好\N{\fs24\1c}maybe these matters would be better handled here,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.62,0:25:18.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这里会受到影响\N{\fs24\1c}where their effects are felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.19,0:25:22.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那梅兰妮·卡维尔怎么办\N{\fs24\1c}And what about Melanie Cavill?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.75,0:25:28.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她会是第一个下台的人\N{\fs24\1c}She'd be the first to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.00,0:25:34.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们是在谈论煽动叛乱的事\N{\fs24\1c}So they're talking about sedition.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.65,0:25:38.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,指挥官是怎么回应的\N{\fs24\1c}How did the commander respond?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.67,0:25:42.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他持中立态度\N{\fs24\1c}Uh, well, he didn't agree or -- or disagree.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.28,0:25:46.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他主要是冷眼看着我们\N{\fs24\1c}He mostly just, uh, stared at us coldly,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.93,0:25:49.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我得说 很有效果\N{\fs24\1c}which, I won't lie, is very effective.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.43,0:25:53.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不用去参加庭审吗\N{\fs24\1c}Don't you need to get to the trial?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.42,0:25:57.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去的\N{\fs24\1c}I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.68,0:26:00.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会加快为你翻修\N{\fs24\1c}We'll speed up those renovations for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.79,0:26:03.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威尔福德先生感谢你的服务\N{\fs24\1c}and Mr. Wilford thanks you for your service.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.10,0:26:19.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲爱的 该走了\N{\fs24\1c}Honey. It's time to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.47,0:26:22.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记得要进行眼神交流\N{\fs24\1c}Make eye contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.53,0:26:24.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fs24\1c}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.19,0:26:25.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-真诚点 -我知道\N{\fs24\1c}- Be sincere. - I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.72,0:26:27.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-老套的眼泪攻势就行 -不要眼泪攻势\N{\fs24\1c}- Trite tears are okay. - Not trite tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.65,0:26:29.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-眼泪攻势 -我会哭出眼泪 不会说出眼泪\N{\fs24\1c}- Contrite tears. - Well, I'll be crying them, not saying them,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.88,0:26:31.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样你可以结束后再来批评我\N{\fs24\1c}so you can just criticize me after.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.04,0:26:33.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来 我的两个莱拉\N{\fs24\1c}Come here, my Liliahs.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.94,0:26:55.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全体起立\N{\fs24\1c}All rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.27,0:27:07.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肃静\N{\fs24\1c}Please settle.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.98,0:27:11.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都知道\N{\fs24\1c}As we are all aware,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.84,0:27:15.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当永动机的秩序遭到犯罪 阴谋和渎职威胁时\N{\fs24\1c}tribunals are convened when the Order of our Eternal Engine
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.80,0:27:21.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会就召开审判\N{\fs24\1c}is threatened by crime, conspiracy, or negligence.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.59,0:27:23.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小莱拉·福爵\N{\fs24\1c}Lilah Folger Junior,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.95,0:27:27.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你被控犯下两起谋杀案\N{\fs24\1c}you stand accused of two counts of murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.70,0:27:30.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请坐\N{\fs24\1c}Please be seated.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.42,0:27:34.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,审判开始\N{\fs24\1c}This tribunal is now in session.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.38,0:27:40.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被告被捕后\N{\fs24\1c}Once the accused was apprehended,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.89,0:27:44.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,司闸员就彻底搜查了\N{\fs24\1c}the Brakemen conducted a full and thorough search
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.11,0:27:46.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,福爵的住处\N{\fs24\1c}of the Folgers' quarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.84,0:27:52.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们找到了本案中最关键的证据\N{\fs24\1c}There we found the most striking evidence in the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.71,0:28:02.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小莱拉的首饰盒里\N{\fs24\1c}Hidden in Lilah Junior's jewelry box
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.62,0:28:04.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藏着保存完好的\N{\fs24\1c}were the particularly preserved
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.96,0:28:09.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两名死者切割下来的生殖器\N{\fs24\1c}severed penises of two male victims.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.86,0:28:15.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肖恩·怀斯被一根细带捆绑\N{\fs24\1c}Sean Wise was bound and choked multiple times
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.17,0:28:16.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并掐至窒息多次\N{\fs24\1c}with a thin ligature.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.16,0:28:21.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的生殖器被切下时...\N{\fs24\1c}He was very much alive when his genitals were...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.49,0:28:23.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他还活着\N{\fs24\1c}chopped off.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.39,0:28:27.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那场景真是惨绝人寰\N{\fs24\1c}It was nothing you ever want to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.89,0:28:31.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他冰冷的尸身就这么盯着我\N{\fs24\1c}He was staring back at me through the cold,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.70,0:28:34.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有四肢\N{\fs24\1c}limbless and...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.11,0:28:37.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有下体\N{\fs24\1c}...and dickless.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.46,0:28:42.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,埃里克一直关注的都是小莱拉\N{\fs24\1c}The whole time, Erik's focus was Lilah Junior.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.26,0:28:45.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我虽然是他的人质 但也几乎是她的人质\N{\fs24\1c}I was as much her hostage as I was his.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.74,0:28:56.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是埃里克和小莱一直以来想要的\N{\fs24\1c}That was what they wanted, Erik and LJ,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.66,0:28:59.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们死于虚妄的愤怒中\N{\fs24\1c}to kill us all in a nihilistic rage.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.94,0:29:04.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是永动机还在\N{\fs24\1c}But the Eternal Engine is still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.25,0:29:11.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来 请夜车的奥德丽小姐\N{\fs24\1c}We will now hear from Miss Audrey of the Nightcar,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.90,0:29:14.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,代表一位被害人发言\N{\fs24\1c}speaking on behalf of one of the victims.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.54,0:29:20.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我将知无不言\N{\fs24\1c}I will tell the whole truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.22,0:29:24.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的名字不叫"被害人"\N{\fs24\1c}Her name was not "Victim."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.97,0:29:29.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她叫妮克莱特·吉奈特 妮基\N{\fs24\1c}Her name was Nicolette Genêt -- Nikki.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.50,0:29:33.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她唱歌跑调 还很善良\N{\fs24\1c}She sang off-key, and she was kind as a rule,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.01,0:29:35.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你们几乎都不在乎她\N{\fs24\1c}but few of you care up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.08,0:29:38.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对你们来说 她只是后车厢的一个死去的女孩\N{\fs24\1c}To you, she's just some dead girl from downtrain.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.20,0:29:43.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们需要关注三等厢的人\N{\fs24\1c}Well, you need to care about the lives of Third,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.09,0:29:47.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们每周七天 每天三班倒\N{\fs24\1c}because seven days a week, three shifts a day,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.57,0:29:50.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保持轴承润滑 防止严寒霜冻\N{\fs24\1c}we keep the bearings greased and the cold at bay.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.50,0:29:53.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们生孩子需要抽签\N{\fs24\1c}We draw straws to have children,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.92,0:29:56.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会死于可预防的意外\N{\fs24\1c}and we die from preventible accidents
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.89,0:29:58.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们能轻松治好的病 却能要我们的命\N{\fs24\1c}and diseases you get treatment for.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.49,0:30:03.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来这里费了不少周折\N{\fs24\1c}I haven't come to this place easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.84,0:30:04.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们离开芝加哥时\N{\fs24\1c}When we left Chicago,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.99,0:30:08.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要威尔福德先生的铁律才能活下来\N{\fs24\1c}we needed Mr. Wilford's iron order to survive,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.18,0:30:12.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但在绕了近19圈后\N{\fs24\1c}but almost 19 revolutions later...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.98,0:30:17.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七年了 我了解你们所有人\N{\fs24\1c}seven years, I know all of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.90,0:30:22.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道 我们需要拯救我们的灵魂\N{\fs24\1c}and I know we need to save our souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.99,0:30:26.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找回你们的同情心\N{\fs24\1c}Find your compassion.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.04,0:30:28.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向列车上所有人发出一条信息\N{\fs24\1c}Send a message to this entire train
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.59,0:30:30.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正义不只属于富人\N{\fs24\1c}that justice is not reserved for the rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.30,0:30:34.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人人都能得到正义 妮基也能\N{\fs24\1c}There can be justice for all, for Nikki.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.42,0:30:36.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的名字是妮基\N{\fs24\1c}Her name was Nikki.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.54,0:30:42.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肃静\N{\fs24\1c}Order!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.98,0:30:48.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肃静 拜托\N{\fs24\1c}Order! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.07,0:30:51.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们稍作休息\N{\fs24\1c}We will take a brief recess,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.69,0:30:54.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回来后 我们将有请被告发言\N{\fs24\1c}and when we return, we will hear from the accused.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.52,0:31:02.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大夫 我能帮囚犯擦地板吗\N{\fs24\1c}Oh, Doctor, can I swab the floor for the prisoners?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.08,0:31:04.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了 我想回到庭审上去\N{\fs24\1c}No, it's okay. I want to get back to the trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.72,0:31:06.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 可怜的姑娘\N{\fs24\1c}Oh, yeah. Poor girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.09,0:31:08.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚有去听吗 抱歉\N{\fs24\1c}Were you listening? Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.73,0:31:10.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真令人心碎\N{\fs24\1c}It's heartbreaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.93,0:31:12.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 确实是\N{\fs24\1c}Thank you. Yes, it really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.11,0:31:25.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用点力\N{\fs24\1c}Come on. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.31,0:31:33.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来\N{\fs24\1c}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.65,0:31:40.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们好 可怜虫们\N{\fs24\1c}Hello, you poor buggers.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.58,0:31:42.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在哪个抽屉里\N{\fs24\1c}Which one's he in?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.15,0:31:43.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己找\N{\fs24\1c}Figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.98,0:31:46.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死\N{\fs24\1c}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.27,0:31:52.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定有名单吧\N{\fs24\1c}There's -- There's got to be a list here somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.97,0:31:58.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快来\N{\fs24\1c}Come on. Quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.09,0:32:12.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么 你们去哪\N{\fs24\1c}What's that? Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.74,0:32:13.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 车尾人\N{\fs24\1c}Sorry, Tailie.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.51,0:32:15.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们趁火打劫\N{\fs24\1c}You're robbing the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.73,0:32:18.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能帮我找到他吗 拜托了\N{\fs24\1c}Can you help me find him, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.50,0:32:19.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不是针对你\N{\fs24\1c}Don't take this personally, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.95,0:32:22.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别被抓了\N{\fs24\1c}And don't get caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.61,0:32:23.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 等下\N{\fs24\1c}No, wait, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.89,0:32:24.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得走了\N{\fs24\1c}Got to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.41,0:32:28.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靠\N{\fs24\1c}Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.85,0:32:37.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莱拉\N{\fs24\1c}Lilah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.56,0:32:43.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管你在暗地里做什么 都别做了\N{\fs24\1c}Whatever you're doing behind closed doors, don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.16,0:32:50.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我给你讲个福爵家的故事\N{\fs24\1c}Let me tell you a Folger family story.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.21,0:32:54.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小莱7岁的时候 她取出了罗伯特的眼睛\N{\fs24\1c}When LJ was 7, she put out Robert's eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.33,0:32:59.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用叉子在他脸上乱戳\N{\fs24\1c}Lashed out with a fork and punctured it all over his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.81,0:33:04.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使胶状物从他脸上流下\N{\fs24\1c}And even as the jelly was running down his cheek,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.01,0:33:08.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在她发脾气的时候全程抱着她 保护她\N{\fs24\1c}he held her through the tantrum, protecting her.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.11,0:33:14.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你继续进行你乘客服务部的走过场审判\N{\fs24\1c}So you go ahead with your Hospitality show trial
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.81,0:33:18.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时后果自负\N{\fs24\1c}and prepare to suffer the consequences.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.22,0:33:23.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你惹的是我的血脉\N{\fs24\1c}Because you're messing with my bloodline.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.49,0:33:30.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借过\N{\fs24\1c}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.13,0:33:42.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在哪 莱顿\N{\fs24\1c}Where are you, Layton?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.13,0:33:46.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在哪\N{\fs24\1c}Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.28,0:33:51.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我发誓会说实话\N{\fs24\1c}I swear to tell the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.74,0:34:02.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱埃里克·索托\N{\fs24\1c}I-I loved Erik Sotto.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.78,0:34:08.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者说至少我认为是这样\N{\fs24\1c}Or at least I think I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.43,0:34:15.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我内心的困惑 疼痛和恐惧\N{\fs24\1c}The -- The confusion, the ache in my guts, the fear,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.24,0:34:17.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是爱 不是吗\N{\fs24\1c}that is love, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.58,0:34:22.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,埃里克跟我说是的\N{\fs24\1c}Erik told me it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.58,0:34:30.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,埃里克控制着我 而我...\N{\fs24\1c}Erik had a power over me, and I --
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.81,0:34:35.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他让我看着他做可怕的事情\N{\fs24\1c}He made me watch him do terrible things.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.66,0:34:41.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我仍能听到那些男人求他住手\N{\fs24\1c}And I-I can still hear those men begging for it to end.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.01,0:34:49.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但埃里克说恐惧让人诚实\N{\fs24\1c}Uh, but Erik said fear makes people honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.82,0:34:51.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想那是真的\N{\fs24\1c}I think that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.40,0:34:59.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肖恩·怀斯 在他死前 他说他是一个线人\N{\fs24\1c}Sean Wise, just before he died, said that he was an informant...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.40,0:35:02.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是威尔福德先生的间谍\N{\fs24\1c}...A spy for Mr. Wilford.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.34,0:35:04.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,见鬼\N{\fs24\1c}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.26,0:35:05.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老天啊\N{\fs24\1c}Dios mío.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.82,0:35:08.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肖恩说阴影和谎言\N{\fs24\1c}Sean said that shadows and lies
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.32,0:35:12.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,占据了我们美丽的列车 从头至尾\N{\fs24\1c}were taking over our beautiful train from tip to Tail,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.35,0:35:15.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从农业区到抽屉间\N{\fs24\1c}from Ag-Sec to The Drawers.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.76,0:35:20.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说"400个能震惊我们所有人的秘密"\N{\fs24\1c}"400 secrets that rock us to the rails," He said,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.63,0:35:21.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他绝不会说出来\N{\fs24\1c}but he would never spill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.92,0:35:28.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米娅\N{\fs24\1c}Mia?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.91,0:35:34.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米娅 我的天\N{\fs24\1c}Mia. Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.28,0:35:37.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这段话我能说给威尔福德先生吗\N{\fs24\1c}Can I say this part to Mr. Wilford?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.42,0:35:40.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以 他有在听\N{\fs24\1c}Yes, he's following along.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.89,0:35:52.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很抱歉我有参与此次悲剧\N{\fs24\1c}I am so sorry for the part that I played in this tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.19,0:35:55.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在本该发声的时候选择了沉默\N{\fs24\1c}I was silent when I should have spoken,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.81,0:35:59.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但肖恩·怀斯为了拯救黑暗中的人类\N{\fs24\1c}but Sean Wise gave his life to save humanity
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.75,0:36:03.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而牺牲了自己 那黑暗差点将我吞噬\N{\fs24\1c}from the darkness that almost swallowed me whole.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.08,0:36:06.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不 不\N{\fs24\1c}Oh, no. No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.96,0:36:10.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果列车能宽恕我\N{\fs24\1c}If the train shows me mercy...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.84,0:36:17.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我保证我也会为它做出贡献\N{\fs24\1c}...I promise to do my part for her, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.65,0:36:23.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只能说这么多\N{\fs24\1c}That's all I can say.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.13,0:36:25.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全体起立\N{\fs24\1c}All rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.11,0:36:30.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,审判员现在将去进行商讨\N{\fs24\1c}The tribunal will now break to deliberate.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.48,0:36:49.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莱顿\N{\fs24\1c}Layton.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.08,0:36:59.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才怎么回事\N{\fs24\1c}What the hell was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.83,0:37:00.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fs24\1c}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.28,0:37:02.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是说\N{\fs24\1c}I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.91,0:37:08.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许肖恩发现抽屉是在做实验\N{\fs24\1c}Maybe Sean found out that The Drawers are experimental.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.98,0:37:11.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许他跟她说了名单\N{\fs24\1c}Maybe he told her about the list.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.92,0:37:13.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就改变了一切 对吗\N{\fs24\1c}Well, that changes the calculus, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.08,0:37:50.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这都怪她\N{\fs24\1c}This is all her fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.11,0:37:52.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从一开始 我就不该来这儿\N{\fs24\1c}From the beginning, I shouldn't even be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.87,0:37:53.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴 哈维尔\N{\fs24\1c}Shut up, Javier.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.30,0:37:55.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有其他选择吗\N{\fs24\1c}Do you have another option?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.75,0:37:56.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有\N{\fs24\1c}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.35,0:37:59.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我没有\N{\fs24\1c}No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.87,0:38:02.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又没和她睡 对吗\N{\fs24\1c}I'm not sleeping with her, am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.89,0:38:09.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莱顿\N{\fs24\1c}Layton?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.52,0:38:13.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莱顿 我来了 莱顿\N{\fs24\1c}Layton, I'm here. Layton.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.08,0:38:28.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莱顿 莱顿 莱顿\N{\fs24\1c}Layton, Layton, Layton.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.48,0:38:29.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莱顿 我来了\N{\fs24\1c}Layton, I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.47,0:38:34.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二等厢走廊真香啊\N{\fs24\1c}Oh, the sweet smell of Second Class corridors.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.15,0:38:36.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的结婚新家\N{\fs24\1c}Your new bridal home, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.97,0:38:39.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吃晚餐吧\N{\fs24\1c}Come for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.29,0:38:42.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二等厢每晚都能有甜点\N{\fs24\1c}Second Class rations get dessert every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.43,0:38:46.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fs24\1c}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.83,0:39:09.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥斯维勒\N{\fs24\1c}Osweiller.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.31,0:39:26.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-莱顿 -是车尾人\N{\fs24\1c}- Layton. - It's a Tailie!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.87,0:39:32.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小奥 小奥 放开她\N{\fs24\1c}Oz! Oz, get off her!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.26,0:39:38.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是提尔 对吗 莱顿\N{\fs24\1c}You're Till, right? Layton.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.59,0:39:40.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-他怎么在这儿 -他几乎没有心跳\N{\fs24\1c}- Why is he in here? - His heartbeat's barely there.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.68,0:39:42.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他应该在车尾的\N{\fs24\1c}He's supposed to be in the Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.13,0:39:49.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莱顿 莱顿\N{\fs24\1c}Layton. Layton.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.90,0:39:50.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莱顿 你能听到我吗\N{\fs24\1c}Layton, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.93,0:39:53.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莱顿 莱顿 是我 莱顿\N{\fs24\1c}Layton. Layton. It's me. Layton.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.90,0:39:55.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莱顿 莱顿\N{\fs24\1c}Layton, Layton.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.98,0:39:56.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莱顿\N{\fs24\1c}Layton.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.76,0:39:59.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得赶紧离开\N{\fs24\1c}We got to get out of here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.43,0:40:01.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肃静\N{\fs24\1c}Order!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.47,0:40:02.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请安静\N{\fs24\1c}Quiet, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.97,0:40:09.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小莱拉·福爵\N{\fs24\1c}Lilah Folger Junior,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.70,0:40:12.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法庭现在将宣布裁决结果\N{\fs24\1c}the tribunal will now announce your verdict.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.34,0:40:16.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陪审团一致决定\N{\fs24\1c}By unanimous decision,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.00,0:40:21.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们认为小莱拉·福爵\N{\fs24\1c}we find Lilah Folger Junior...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.72,0:40:24.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有罪名都成立\N{\fs24\1c}guilty on all counts.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.82,0:40:53.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别无他法\N{\fs24\1c}There's no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.47,0:40:57.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是她在最坏情况下的要求\N{\fs24\1c}It's what she asked for in the worst case.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.69,0:40:59.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她就不该管的\N{\fs24\1c}She should've left it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.88,0:41:02.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她就不该管的\N{\fs24\1c}She should've just left it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.40,0:41:19.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肃静 肃静\N{\fs24\1c}Order! Order!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.80,0:41:24.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家肃静\N{\fs24\1c}Order, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.95,0:41:27.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们收到了一条威尔福德先生的信息\N{\fs24\1c}We have a message from Mr. Wilford.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.06,0:41:35.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,考虑到被告还很年轻\N{\fs24\1c}In light of the young age of the accused...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.42,0:41:41.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威尔福德先生选择减免小莱拉·福爵的判决\N{\fs24\1c}...Mr. Wilford commutes the sentence of Lilah Folger Junior
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.51,0:41:44.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将她送还给她的父母\N{\fs24\1c}and remands her to the custody of her parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.23,0:41:49.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢天谢地 你安全了\N{\fs24\1c}Thank God. You're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.38,0:41:52.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请冷静\N{\fs24\1c}Please calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.33,0:41:56.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肃静 肃静\N{\fs24\1c}Order! Order! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.55,0:41:58.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家保持冷静\N{\fs24\1c}Everyone remain calm!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.07,0:42:03.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请保持冷静 庭审结束\N{\fs24\1c}Please remain calm! This trial is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.33,0:42:06.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请保持冷静\N{\fs24\1c}Please remain calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.47,0:42:26.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 我只能到这儿了\N{\fs24\1c}Alright. As far as I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.54,0:42:27.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-什么 -我得走了\N{\fs24\1c}- What? - No, I got to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.83,0:42:29.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你去哪 -我就是得走了\N{\fs24\1c}- Where are you going? - Just -- I got to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.48,0:42:31.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-在哪 -继续走\N{\fs24\1c}- Where is it? - Keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.76,0:42:32.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她就在前面\N{\fs24\1c}She's down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.56,0:42:34.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 莱顿\N{\fs24\1c}Come on, Layton.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.58,0:42:39.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我扶着你 我扶着你\N{\fs24\1c}I've got you. I've got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.75,0:42:47.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乔茜\N{\fs24\1c}Josie.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.87,0:42:50.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得把他藏起来\N{\fs24\1c}You need to hide him.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.08,0:42:52.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他怎么了\N{\fs24\1c}What's wrong with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.90,0:42:54.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们把他关进了抽屉\N{\fs24\1c}They drawered him.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.08,0:43:00.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不准抛下我 好吗\N{\fs24\1c}Don't you give up on me now, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.92,0:43:02.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会回来的\N{\fs24\1c}I'll be back. I'll be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.90,0:43:03.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会回来的\N{\fs24\1c}I'll be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.15,0:43:05.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么从车尾出来的\N{\fs24\1c}How'd you get out of the Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.18,0:43:14.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,车尾需要信任你 扎拉\N{\fs24\1c}The Tail needs to trust you, Zarah.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.02,0:43:16.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会照顾他的\N{\fs24\1c}I'll look after him.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.82,0:43:28.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得送你到楼上去\N{\fs24\1c}Got to get you upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.98,0:43:34.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我放你回到你父母身边之前\N{\fs24\1c}Before I release you to your parents...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.24,0:43:38.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威尔福德先生要我\N{\fs24\1c}Mr. Wilford has asked me
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.56,0:43:42.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,强调守口如瓶的重要性\N{\fs24\1c}to stress the importance of discretion.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.40,0:43:46.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别把他的抽屉秘密说出去\N{\fs24\1c}Oh, so don't spill all of his Drawer secrets?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.37,0:43:53.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肖恩·怀斯具体跟你说了什么\N{\fs24\1c}What did Sean Wise tell you exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.19,0:43:57.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我和威尔福德先生之间的事 不是吗\N{\fs24\1c}That's between me and Mr. Wilford, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.88,0:44:03.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他为了帮你冒了很大的风险\N{\fs24\1c}He's taking an extraordinary risk in helping you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.67,0:44:05.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三等厢\N{\fs24\1c}Third Class?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.63,0:44:07.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们会翻篇的\N{\fs24\1c}I think they'll get over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.10,0:44:11.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是说你 小莱\N{\fs24\1c}I mean you, LJ.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.92,0:44:15.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我指的是放你走\N{\fs24\1c}I mean letting you walk free.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.99,0:44:25.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威尔福德关照我\N{\fs24\1c}Wilford looked out for me, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.39,0:44:28.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也会关照他\N{\fs24\1c}I'll look out for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.64,0:44:34.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能走了吗\N{\fs24\1c}Can I go now?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.27,0:44:56.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-爸爸 -莱拉\N{\fs24\1c}- Daddy! - Lilah.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.92,0:44:57.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结束了\N{\fs24\1c}It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.20,0:44:59.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你安全了 -都结束了\N{\fs24\1c}- You're safe. - It's all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.08,0:45:04.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-真是场噩梦 -你安全了\N{\fs24\1c}- What a nightmare. - You're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.32,0:45:07.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱你\N{\fs24\1c}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.11,0:45:12.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥斯维勒\N{\fs24\1c}Osweiller?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.58,0:45:17.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死\N{\fs24\1c}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.84,0:45:55.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下不为例\N{\fs24\1c}Never again.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.46,0:45:57.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-下不为例 -下不为例\N{\fs24\1c}- Never again. - Never again.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.95,0:45:59.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-下不为例 -下不为例\N{\fs24\1c}- Never again. - Never again.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.37,0:46:00.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-下不为例 -下不为例\N{\fs24\1c}- Never again. - Never again.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.98,0:46:02.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-下不为例 -下不为例\N{\fs24\1c}- Never again. - Never again.
